      "Middleware/interceptor — add latency instrumentation for all outbound HTTP calls",
      "Circuit breaker configuration — add per-dependency circuit breakers",
      "Geocoding client — add caching layer (Redis or in-memory with TTL)",
      "Request orchestration — parallelize independent external calls"
